{"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/objc(cs)NSObject"],"type":"inheritsFrom","title":"Inherits From","kind":"relationships"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/objc(pl)NSObject","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/s7CVarArgP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/s28CustomDebugStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/s23CustomStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/Se","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SE","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SQ","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SH"],"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Field validation status."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"(SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Optical character recognition (OCR) invariably introduces errors in the recognized text."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"There are numerous ways to verify that what has been recognized is, in fact, what was"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"written in the document."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The best way to validate the value of a field is for it to have a known format or validation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"logic. For example, an IBAN number has a known format and two check digits that make it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"very unlikely that a value with OCR errors will pass validation. Fields with known"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"validation rules will have a validation status of either VALID or INVALID."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Fields whose value can be inferred from other fields, or from domain knowledge (for example,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the field may have the same value in every instance of this type of document), will have the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"status INFERRED. Inferring the value of a field is a strong validation method, provided that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"there are no unexpected changes to the document format."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Fields that do not have validation rules and cannot be inferred can still be validated by checking whether the same","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value is recognized from multiple attempts, e.g. across multiple frames of a camera stream.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If the same value is recognized in multiple frames, the value is considered CONFIRMED, otherwise","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it will have the status NONE. This is the least strict validation method, as it does not protect","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"from systemic OCR errors, but in practice it still provides good results for most fields."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","title":"SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus","kind":"identifier"}]},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/rawValue"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/confirmed","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/ignored","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/inferred","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/invalid","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/none","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/obstructed","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/valid"],"generated":true,"title":"Type Properties","anchor":"Type-Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/enumValue(from:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Type Methods","anchor":"Type-Methods"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sb