reby confirming the value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Occurs only for fields that have no validation rules otherwise.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A CONFIRMED value gives a strong guarantee that the field value has been read out without errors,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"but not as strong as VALID. The value may still be incorrect, due to systemic OCR errors.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In case of OCR errors, increase the number of frames needed to confirm the value in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"recognizer configuration."}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkgenericdocumentfieldvalidationstatus\/confirmed","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/confirmed"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus/enumValue(from:)":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkgenericdocumentfieldvalidationstatus\/enumvalue(from:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus\/enumValue(from:)","abstract":[{"text":"Returns an instance of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKGenericDocumentFieldValidationStatus","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" based on the provided raw value.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"enumValue"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"from"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},